We all love a lekker local getaway, but sometimes the real thrill lies beyond the border. From tropical island escapes like Mauritius and Zanzibar to wild African wonders like Vic Falls, Windhoek, and Harare, we’ve spread our wings to bring you even more magic beyond Mzansi. 

Whether you’re craving palm trees and cocktails, roaring waterfalls and wildlife, or sunsets over desert sands, we’ve got the adventure you’ve been dreaming of. 

Get your passports ready and visit www.flysafair.co.za

T's&C's apply

Throwback to an unforgettable moment! Last month, we handed over the keys to a brand-new Citroen C5 Aircross SUV worth R361,900 to our lucky winner, Bathabile Mashinini!

Congratulations again, Bathabile!

#ThrowBackThursday #CarGiveaway #FlySafair #FirstCarRental

Congratulations to Shenique Miny, you are the lucky winner of our George-ous getaway prize to George. 

Get ready for adventure - the stunning forests, beaches, lagoons, and mountains of the Garden Route await. We hope you have a great time!

At FlySafair, we’re all about low-cost, comfort, and convenience. That’s why we are binning our overhead bins and introducing more spacious cabins, which not only means a comfier ride, but also faster, fuel-smart flying. Of course, this does mean no more hand luggage and a nominal fee to check that extra bag—a small price to pay for no more sky-high smacks on the head or a carry-on avalanche upon landing. 

As of 1 April, we’re loading up on extra overhead space to make each of our domestic flights that much extra! Now that’s being a step ahead of the rest. 

#FlySafair #NoMoreOverheadBins #NoMoreHandLuggage #SpaciousCabins #MoreComfort #AprilFools

Love flying with nifty innovations that make your travel as hassle-free as can be! Plans changed last minute? No worries, we give you the flexibility to adjust your booking right up until 1.5 hours before departure. 

Hate second guessing? Track your plane in real-time in our app and share its location with friends and family. We also send you airport traffic alerts so you can avoid the rush and check in with ease. All this, plus a friendly crew that’s always ready to welcome you!

Love flying, book now at www.flysafair.co.za
